---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="New Authority Trucking Insurance | Get Covered Fast | RMS"
  description="Just got your trucking authority? We help new owner-operators get insured fast with coverage that makes sense. Call 208-800-0640 for a quote."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc 0%, #004499 100%); color: white; padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">New Authority? Let's Get You Covered Right.</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; opacity: 0.9;">
        Getting your authority is hard enough. We make insurance the easy part.
      </p>
      <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 16px 32px; background: white; color: #0066cc;">
        Talk to Someone Who Gets It: 208-800-0640
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- We Know What You're Dealing With -->
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">We Know What You're Dealing With</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">You just got your authority (or you're about to). Congratulations - and welcome to the chaos:</p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #666;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">DOT filings and compliance paperwork</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Finding your first loads on the boards</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Figuring out which brokers to trust</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Managing cash flow before the money starts flowing</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Learning the difference between a good rate and a trap</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>And now... figuring out insurance</strong></li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color: #666;">One more thing on the pile. We get it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We'll Do -->
  <section style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Here's What We'll Do</h2>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Walk You Through What You Actually Need</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">New authority insurance isn't complicated, but nobody explains it clearly. We will.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Required:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #666;">
          <li>Auto Liability (BI/PD) - minimum $750K, most need $1M</li>
          <li>Cargo Insurance - required for most freight</li>
          <li>FMCSA filings (we handle this)</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Smart to Have:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #666;">
          <li>Physical Damage (if you're financing)</li>
          <li>Non-Trucking Liability (bobtail)</li>
          <li>Occupational Accident</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Get You Quoted Fast</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">You need to get moving. We'll get you options quickly so you can start running loads.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Be Here When You Have Questions</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">You will have questions. That's normal. And we'll actually answer the phone.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Common New Authority Questions</h2>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">How much is this going to cost?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">New authority insurance is expensive - typically $12,000-$20,000/year for liability alone. That's the reality. It goes down after you build history.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Can I get a lower price somewhere else?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">Probably not. We all have access to the same 3-4 carriers that write new authorities. The rates are basically the same. The difference is service.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">How long until I'm covered?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">Once you accept a quote and pay, coverage can bind same day. Filings typically process within 24-48 hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 4rem 0; text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; opacity: 0.9;">Call us - we answer.</p>
      <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.5rem; padding: 20px 40px; background: white; color: #0066cc;">
        208-800-0640
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
